data.eml:eml: A check-list of Ensifera from Algeria (Insecta: Orthoptera)

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Desutter-Grandcolas, Laure (2010): A check-list of Ensifera from Algeria (Insecta: Orthoptera). Zootaxa 2432: 1-44, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.294257
